Instead, a helper in `rpc/util.{h,cpp}` (or `rpc/fees.h`) could be added such as:

```cpp
enum class FeeRateUnit { BTC_KVB, SAT_VB };
UniValue ValueFromFeeRate(const CFeeRate& fr, FeeRateUnit unit);
```

